                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970920-63-off333 t17970920-63-cd334"></join>, fifteen yards of printed cotton, value 38s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17970920-63-victim482" type="victimName">
